description: Kunjiam Ski Resort is only a 40-minute drive from Gangnam, Seoul. The resort has ski resorts, spas, golf and other auxiliary facilities. It is a comprehensive resort. Kunjiam Ski Resort has a total of 9 ski runs and 5 lift lines, and the average width of the ski runs is more than 100 meters. It is the largest ski resort in Gyeonggi-do. A 1.8-kilometer-long ski run in the resort is a highlight for beginners and intermediate skiers.
